Version: 0.1.22
Date: 2026-04-14

Changes:
- WeChat progress push behavior:
  - disable per-turn progress push by default.
  - WeChat now sends final reply only unless explicitly enabled.
  - `MERLION_WECHAT_PROGRESS=1` enables per-turn progress.
  - `MERLION_WECHAT_PROGRESS_VERBOSE=1` keeps tool-batch detail when progress mode is enabled.
- Tests:
  - update unit tests for new progress default.
- Docs:
  - update README and feature notes to reflect final-reply-only default.

Related commits:
- feat(wechat): default final-reply-only, opt-in progress push
